OL,3,CRugby player, 28, dies after
OL,4,Ccollapsing at half marathon
OL,6,FA 28-year-old rugby player has died
OL,7,Fafter collapsing at the Great Bristol
OL,8,FRun.
OL,10,FJon Devereux, from Chester, was taking
OL,11,Fpart in the half marathon race on 11
OL,12,FMay when he fell ill. He then received
OL,13,Fmedical treatment at the scene but
OL,14,Fdied in hospital.
OL,16,FIn a statement released on 12 May,
OL,17,Frace organisers confirmed the news and
OL,18,Fsaid they extended their "heartfelt
OL,19,Fcondolences" to Mr Devereux's family.
